<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id90489210-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s3783"><num value="3783">§ 3783.</num><heading> Disposition of property of United States</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No property of the United States located in the Republic of Panama may be disposed of except pursuant to law enacted by the Congress.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id90489211-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/96/70/tI/s1503">Pub. L. 96–70, title I, § 1503</ref>, <date date="1979-09-27">Sept. 27, 1979</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/93/488">93 Stat. 488</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
